test_rough_stack2 = 'rough_input_stack_2'
with open(FILE_ROUGH_TILES, 'r') as f:
    j = json.load(f)
tilespecs = [renderapi.tilespec.TileSpec(json=d) for d in j]
renderapi.stack.create_stack(test_rough_stack2, render=render)
renderapi.client.import_tilespecs(test_rough_stack2, tilespecs, render=
    render, use_rest=True)
z_values = renderapi.stack.get_z_values_for_stack(test_rough_stack2, render
    =render)
renderapi.stack.delete_section(test_rough_stack2, z_values[3], render=render)
renderapi.stack.set_stack_state(test_rough_stack2, 'COMPLETE', render=render)
yield test_rough_stack2
renderapi.stack.delete_stack(test_rough_stack2, render=render)
pytest.fixture(scope='module')
